<%- include("../partials/header") %>
<!-- Jumbotron -->
<div class="jumbotron yellow">
    <section>
        <h1 class="mb-3">My Work</h1> 
        <p class="work mb-5">I can help you through the whole design process
        to find the best solution that fits your needs</p>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <div class="row">
                    <a class="work-light" href="/mywork/product"><div class="mx-3 work-active">Product Design<hr class="work-active"></div></a>
                    <a class="work-light" href="/mywork/jewelry"><div class="mx-3">Jewelry Design</div></a>
                    <a class="work-light" href="/mywork/graphic"><div class="mx-3">Graphic Design</div></a>
                    <a class="work-light" href="/mywork/ux"><div class="mx-3">UX/UI Design</div></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

<section>
    <!-- pop up Research -->
    <div class="popup" onclick="research()">
        <p class="popuptext product-research" id="research" onclick="research()">
            Primary and secondary research about the user, market, company, competitors,
            trends, materials and more in order to find insights about user's needs desires and market gaps
            to choose the best approach design wise.
        </p>
    </div>
    <!-- pop up Concept -->
    <div class="popup" onclick="concept()">
        <p class="popuptext product-concept" id="concept" onclick="concept()">
            Decide an idea of a product and/or service that can fit the needs of the user and 
            requirements of the client. Tools such as SCAMPER, brainstorming, guidelines map, 
            moodboards and more may be useful to find the concept. Something useful to have in mind 
            are the requirements, which will help us decide the possible materials, processes and 
            channels in which the product and/or service will be manufactured and delivered.
        </p>
    </div>
    <!-- pop up Sketching -->
    <div class="popup" onclick="sketching()">
        <p class="popuptext product-sketching" id="sketching" onclick="sketching()">
            2D sketches are useful because they can be done quickly and give you a general 
            idea of what you are thinking. Combinations and modifications can be made until 
            there is one that satisfies you. Inspirational moodboards may be useful to get a 
            general idea of aesthetic line, look & feel, shapes and materials. 
        </p>
    </div>
    <!-- pop up Prototyping -->
    <div class="popup" onclick="prototyping()">
        <p class="popuptext product-prototyping" id="prototyping" onclick="prototyping()">
            Rapid prototypes are useful because they can be done quickly, yoy don't need
            much material to make them and you can compare between them to see which one 
            you like best. This is not a linear process, you can jump back and forth as much 
            times as you need.
        </p>
    </div>
    <!-- pop up CAD Modeling -->
    <div class="popup" onclick="modeling()">
        <p class="popuptext product-modeling" id="modeling" onclick="modeling()">
            3D Models can be useful to see how the piece will be without having the actual piece.
            With a 3D Model, a render can be made in order to see how the materials and the finishings
            will look in the manufactured piece. Renders work for the client to look how the piece will
            look after manufacturing.
        </p>
    </div>
    <!-- pop up Manufacturing -->
    <div class="popup" onclick="manufacturing()">
        <p class="popuptext product-manufacturing" id="manufacturing" onclick="manufacturing()">
            This is the final step, once you have your sketches and rapid prototypes it's 
            time to decide which material is best for the product, which process if best for 
            manufacturing and which channel is best for delivering the product and/or service.
        </p>
    </div>
    <!-- ends model -->

    <div class="row">
        <!-- Process -->
        <div class="col-3 d-none d-xl-block">
            <p class="m-0"><i class="fas fa-circle icon-yellow"></i>  Research 
                <!-- pop up -->
                <span class="popup" onclick="research()"><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i></span>
            </p>
            <div class="vl"></div>
            <p class="m-0"><i class="fas fa-circle icon-yellow"></i>  Concept 
                <!-- pop up -->
                <span class="popup" onclick="concept()"><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i></span>
            </p>
            <div class="vl"></div>
            <p class="m-0"><i class="fas fa-circle icon-yellow"></i> Sketching 
                <!-- pop up -->
                <span class="popup" onclick="sketching()"><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i></span>
            <div class="vl"></div>
            <p class="m-0"><i class="fas fa-circle icon-yellow"></i> Rapid Prototyping 
                <!-- pop up -->
                <span class="popup" onclick="prototyping()"><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i></span>
            <div class="vl"></div>
            <p class="m-0"><i class="fas fa-circle icon-yellow"></i> 3D Modeling 
                <!-- pop up -->
                <span class="popup" onclick="modeling()"><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i></span>
            <div class="vl"></div>
            <p class="m-0"><i class="fas fa-circle icon-yellow"></i> Manufacturing 
                <!-- pop up -->
                <span class="popup" onclick="manufacturing()"><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i></span>
        </div>
        <!-- Images -->
        <div class="col-12 col-xl-9">
            <div class="row justify-content-between">
                <div class="col-12 col-lg-8 my-3">
                    <a href="/mywork/product/aventure"><img class="show" src="../../imgs/Work/Product/Cover/aventure.jpg" alt=""></a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-6 col-lg-4 my-3">
                    <a href="/mywork/product/dual"><img class="show" src="../../imgs/Work/Product/Cover/dual.jpg" alt=""></a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-6 col-lg-4 my-3">
                    <a href="/mywork/product/pado"><img class="show" src="../../imgs/Work/Product/Cover/pado.jpg" alt=""></a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-6 col-lg-4 my-3">
                    <a href="/mywork/product/dreams"><img class="show" src="../../imgs/Work/Product/Cover/dreams.jpg" alt=""></a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-6 col-lg-4 my-3">
                    <a href="/mywork/product/angular"><img class="show" src="../../imgs/Work/Product/Cover/angular.jpg" alt=""></a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-12 col-lg-8 my-3">
                    <a href="/mywork/product/neo"><img class="show" src="../../imgs/Work/Product/Cover/neo.jpg" alt=""></a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-6 col-lg-4 my-3">
                    <a href="/mywork/product/eternal"><img class="show" src="../../imgs/Work/Product/Cover/eternal.jpg" alt=""></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

